title: Ceal

creator: Affinidi Pte. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Build and manage your digital identity. Receive, store, and share your credentials. Unlock job opportunities by fast-tracking applications. Ceal is powered by Affinidi, a Temasek-founded company.
Ceal is the all-in-one app for professionals like you to create and control your own identity documents, professional and academic certificates, accreditations, testimonials and much more. Explore the world of Ceal using your digital identity to access products and services across industries and geographies, in a secure, transparent, and consent-driven manner.

Recruitment – Breeze through what can sometimes be a long and daunting process just to prove your qualifications. With Ceal, you can simply request for digital proofs from certification-issuing organisations, and share them with hiring managers in a fast and reliable manner.

Education – Obtain verified certifications instantly for each achievement as you progress through your academic journey. Whether it is for a full-time degree or an ad-hoc upskill course, keep them all stored at your fingertips and ready to share when you need them.

Networking – Get smart with networking via your personalised contactless business card. Never forget to carry them again. Forge unlimited connections.
descriptionShort: Ceal is a wallet to store your personal info as “verifiable credentials.”

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We hear you! We have introduced an exciting new interface to enhance your experience as you explore our app

As the world reopens, we have also introduced Business card! You can now issue and share your contact information at conferences and events via QR Code and web links

Bug fixes to improve app performance

Share your digital identity to grow and expand your network!
